    "updated_at": "2012-01-11T22:57:56Z",
    "body": "If you are, could you try changing the \"get_setting\" function in common.py to the following, restart the editor and try again?\r\n \r\n```python\r\n\r\ndef get_setting(key, default=None):\r\n    try:\r\n        s = sublime.active_window().active_view().settings()\r\n        data = s.get(\"sublimeclang_%s\" % key, None)\r\n        if data != None:\r\n            return data\r\n    except:\r\n        pass\r\n    return get_settings().get(key, default)\r\n\r\n```"
  },
